    "plan_content": "## Plan Summary\n\n**Root cause:** Classic off-by-one error in `src/utils.ts` at line 7.\n\n```typescript\n// BUG — stops one iteration early\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length - 1; i++) {\n\n// FIX — processes every element\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length; i++) {\n```\n\nThe `- 1` in the loop bound means for an array of `n` items, only `n-1` items are ever processed — the last element is always skipped.\n\n**Scope:** Single-character change (`- 1` removed) in one file — `src/utils.ts` line 7. No other files need modification.\n\n**Tests:** 3 of the 6 tests are currently failing (`processItems` with 3 items, 2 items, and 1 item). All 6 will pass after the fix.\n\nShall I apply the fix?",
